text: Sorry for the late reply! Hi Michael, thanks for accepting me as a match. :) Hope you are doing well during these times.

Likewise, let me know how exactly you want me to help you :slightly_smiling_face:
If you have any work you want feedback on feel free to send it, if you want to know more about me (what I do and how I got there) i'm also happy to answer those questions
if there is anythign I cant answer i'll tell you, so ask whatever you want :slightly_smiling_face:
